
NEW APP FEATURES
users can sign into the app with their email and password
users can create recipes with ingredients and instructions
recipes can be marked as public or private
users can view other people’s recipes - search
comments
ingredients from recipes can be added to user’s grocery lists
users can create their own occasions and assign recipes to occasions
Sharing with others
Favoriting recipes
Users follow each other
Groups
Group chats
Export to other apps?

TABLES TO STORE INFORMATION
Users info
recipes(hold ingredients & instructions)
Users connections between users - follows
Comments & Likes
messages
Grocery lists (bring in ingredients)
Groups -> group chats
occasions(label) brings in recipes
